<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hu">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sikeres regisztráció – Boxify</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    body, table, td, p, a, li, blockquote { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100% !important; }
    img { border: 0; outline: none; text-decoration: none; -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; }

    /* Fonts */
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5fc;
      color: #373251;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f5f5fc;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .email-container {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #FFFFFF;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(166, 129, 196, 0.10);
    }

    /* Body */
    .email-body {
      padding: 28px 40px 36px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-body h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #323351;
      margin: 20px 0 8px;
    }

    .email-body .greeting {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #71738c;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Info card */
    .info-card {
      background-color: #f4f4fd;
      border: 1px solid #e2e0ef;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .info-card .info-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #75718c;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }

    .info-card .info-value {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #323451;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .info-card .info-value:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    /* Divider */
    .divider {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e1ef;
      margin: 28px 0;
    }

    /* Tips section */
    .tips {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 0 40px 32px;
    }

    .tips h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #323751;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    .tips ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0 0 0 20px;
    }

    .tips ul li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #71748c;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .tips ul li strong {
      color: #323351;
    }

    /* Footer */
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f4f4fd;
      padding: 24px 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e1ef;
    }

    .email-footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #71778c;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .email-footer a {
      color: #5552f7;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .email-footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container { margin: 0 16px; }
      .email-header { padding: 28px 24px 24px; }
      .email-body { padding: 24px 24px 28px; }
      .tips { padding: 0 24px 24px; }
      .email-footer { padding: 20px 24px; }
      .email-header .logo-text { font-size: 24px; }
      .email-body h1 { font-size: 20px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <div class="email-container">

            <!-- Body -->
            <div class="email-body">
              <h1>Sikeres regisztráció! 🎉</h1>
              <p class="greeting">
                Kedves <strong><%= name %></strong>,<br/>
                Üdvözlünk a Boxify családban! A fiókod sikeresen létrejött, és máris kezelheted dobozaid a rendszerünkben.
              </p>

              <!-- User info card -->
              <div class="info-card">
                <p class="info-label">Felhasználónév</p>
                <p class="info-value"><%= name %></p>
                <p class="info-label">E-mail cím</p>
                <p class="info-value"><%= email %></p>
              </div>

              <hr class="divider" />
            </div>

            <!-- Tips -->
            <div class="tips">
              <h3>🚀 Első lépések:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Hozz létre <strong>dobozokat</strong></li>
                <li><strong>Add hozzá</strong> tárgyaidat</li>
                <li><strong>Pakold</strong> őket a dobozokba</li>
                <li><strong>Kövesd</strong> nyomon mit hova pakoltál</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="email-footer">
              <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Boxify – Minden jog fenntartva.</p>
              <p>Ha nem te hoztad létre ezt a fiókot, kérjük <a href="mailto:support@Boxify.hu">jelezd nekünk</a>.</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
